Store Events
July



Anniversary Sale
July 21 - August 06


											Come shop our most popular sale! What sets it apart? For a limited time, we take brand-new, just-arrived styles and offer them to you at super-sale prices. We're talking major savings on the hottest trends and brands for women, men and kids. The event ends on August 6, and all sale items go up to their original prices on August 7.
										




Anniversary Beauty GLAM OUT
July 21 - August 06
12:00 PM - 7:00 PM

											Join us in stores for your daily dose of free samples, gifts with purchase, expert tips—and 300+ Beauty Exclusives.
										



September



ECCO Fall 2017 Event
September 23
12:00 PM - 3:00 PM

											Join us in Women’s Shoes to view the new 2017 Fall ECCO Collection. An ECCO representative will be on hand to answer questions and assist with fitting. Receive a gift with any ECCO purchase. *While supply lasts.
										




St. John Fall 2017 English Garden Event
September 30
12:00 PM - 2:00 PM

											Assemble your own personal floral arrangement at the whimsical St. John Bloom Bar or select an arrangement that is already assembled. Shop the Fall 2017 Collection and receive an exclusive St. John Grey Tote with your regular-priced purchase of $1,500 or more*.

* Valid on regular-priced merchandise purchased on (Saturday, September 30, 2017). Limit one tote per customer.  
Available while supplies last.
										





